Story**
Once upon a time in a forest, there lived a monkey who resided on a berry tree, which was on the banks of the river.
In the same forest, there lived a crocodile and his wife.
One day, the crocodile came to the banks of the river, and rested under the tree.
The kind hearted monkey offered him some fruits.
The crocodile came back the next day for more fruits as he loved them.
As day passed by the crocodile and monkey became good friends.
The monkey sent some fruits and berries to the crocodile's wife as well.
The croceodile's wife liked them very much. but she also wanted to eat the monkey itself.